\[H^{\ell}_{\mathtt{ss}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{\prime}) =\frac{1}{N\mathcal{H}}\bm{h}^{\ell}_{\mathfrak{s}}(\bm{x},t)\cdot \bm{h}^{\ell}_{\mathfrak{s}}(\bm{x},t)\] \[G^{\ell}_{\mathtt{ss}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{ \prime}) =\frac{1}{N\mathcal{H}}\bm{g}^{\ell}_{\mathfrak{s}}(\bm{x},t)\cdot \bm{g}^{\ell}_{\mathfrak{s}}(\bm{x},t)\] \[V^{\ell\sigma}_{\mathtt{ss}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^ {\prime}) =\frac{1}{\mathcal{H}}\sum_{\mathfrak{h}=1}^{\mathcal{H}}\sum_{ \mathfrak{s}^{\prime\prime}\mathfrak{s}^{\prime\prime\prime}}V^{\ell\sigma}_ {\mathtt{bs}^{\prime\prime}\mathfrak{s}^{\prime\prime\prime\prime}}(\bm{x}, \bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{\prime})\sigma^{\ell}_{\mathtt{bs}^{\prime\prime}}(\bm{ x},t)\sigma^{\ell}_{\mathtt{bs}^{\prime\prime\prime\prime}}(\bm{x}^{\prime},t^{ \prime})\]

and many more correlation and response functions. We will call the full collection of all the necessary head-averaged order parameters \(\bm{Q}_{\text{global}}\). Further, not all of the stochastic fields will be relevant to characterize the residual stream. Specifically, only head-averaged fields \(\bar{\chi}^{\ell}_{O},\bar{\xi}^{\ell}_{V},\bar{\xi}^{\ell}_{K},\bar{\xi}^{ \ell}_{Q}\) are relevant. For example, the first of these is defined as

\[\bar{\chi}^{\ell}_{O\mathfrak{s}}(\bm{x},t)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{ \mathcal{H}}}\sum_{\mathfrak{h}=1}^{\mathcal{H}}\sum_{\mathfrak{s}^{\prime} \in[\mathcal{S}]}\sigma^{\ell}_{\mathtt{bs}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},t)\chi^{\ell}_{O \mathfrak{bs}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},t)\] \[=\frac{1}{\sqrt{\mathcal{H}}}\sum_{\mathfrak{h}=1}^{\mathcal{H}} \sum_{\mathfrak{s}^{\prime}\in[\mathcal{S}]}\sigma^{\ell}_{\mathtt{bs}^{ \prime}}(\bm{x},t)\left[u^{\ell}_{O\mathfrak{bs}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},t)+\frac{1}{ \sqrt{\mathcal{H}}}\sum_{t^{\prime}\mathfrak{s}^{\prime\prime}}\int d\bm{x}^{ \prime}R^{v^{\ell},\xi^{\ell}_{O}}_{\mathfrak{bs}^{\prime}\mathfrak{s}^{ \prime\prime}}(\bm{x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{\prime})g^{\ell+1}_{\mathfrak{s}^ {\prime\prime}}(\bm{x}^{\prime},t^{\prime})\right]\] \[=\bar{u}^{\ell}_{O\mathfrak{s}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},t)+\sum_{t^{ \prime}\mathfrak{s}^{\prime}}\int d\bm{x}^{\prime}\bar{R}^{v^{\ell}\xi^{ \ell}_{O}\sigma}_{\mathtt{ss}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{\prime})g ^{\ell+1}_{\mathfrak{s}^{\prime}}(\bm{x}^{\prime},t^{\prime})\] (74)

