\[\bar{u}^{\ell}_{O\mathfrak{s}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},t)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{ \mathcal{H}}}\sum_{\mathfrak{h}=1}^{\mathcal{H}}\sum_{s^{\prime}\in[\mathcal{S} ]}\sigma^{\ell}_{\mathtt{bs}^{\prime}}u^{\ell}_{O\mathfrak{bs}^{\prime}}(\bm{ x},t)\] (75) \[\bar{R}^{v^{\ell}\xi^{\ell}_{O}\sigma}_{\mathtt{ss}^{\prime}}(\bm {x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{\prime})=\frac{1}{\mathcal{H}}\sum_{\mathfrak{h}=1}^{ \mathcal{H}}\sum_{\mathfrak{s}^{\prime\prime}}\sigma^{\ell}_{\mathtt{bs}^{ \prime\prime}}(\bm{x},t)R^{v^{\ell},\xi^{\ell}_{O}}_{\mathfrak{bs}^{\prime \prime}\mathfrak{s}^{\prime}}(\bm{x},\bm{x}^{\prime},t,t^{\prime}).\] (76)

